# Noetfield tracking (agents)

Follow [.cursor/AGENT_TRACKING.md](../AGENT_TRACKING.md).

- **Tasks:** `ops/private/todolist/` if it exists locally; otherwise **GitHub Issues**.
- **Never commit:** `ops/private/`, root `todolist/`, or founder checklists under `docs/`.
- **Public updates only:** [docs/ROADMAP.md](../../docs/ROADMAP.md), code, tests.
